Name: Ultimate - B.P.M
Desc:
Dense PK powers gush forth at a faster speed. If you use up all of your Psychic Points, your telekinesis loses its power, and starts gushing again when you regain a certain number of Psychic Points. Ultimate-B.P.M does not affect enemies in the Damage Reflection status.
Can be toggled On/Off.
Required Skill: Ultimate-Train Level 10

H.Old:
Attacks up to 3 enemies at 175% Damage 7 times. Psychic Point Cost per Activation: 1
Attacks stop when Psychic Points are exhausted, and then resume when 3 or more Psychic Points are restored.
Cooldown: 500 sec.
[Ultimate-Material] damage +310%p
[Ultimate-Deep Impact] damage +270%p
[Ultimate-Train] damage +100%p
H.New:
Attacks up to 3 enemies at 175% Damage 7 times.
Consumes 1 Psychic Point blocks per activation.
Attacks stop when Psychic Points are exhausted, and then resume when 3 or more Psychic Points are restored.
Cooldown: 500 sec.
[Ultimate - Material] Damage +310%p
[Ultimate - Deep Impact] Damage +270%p
[Ultimate - Train] Damage +100%p
